# Build artifacts
/bin/
langstream
*.exe

# Go
*.test
*.out

# Stray zero-byte temp files left behind by gofmt -w on some sandboxed/
# bindfs-mounted filesystems (rename-based atomic write falls back to a
# temp file the OS won't let us unlink there). Harmless - never matched by
# the Go toolchain since they don't end in exactly ".go" - but keep them
# out of git.
*.go.[0-9]*

# OS/editor cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
